MMAM / $MERCH Weekly Sweepstakes Official Rules

**NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. A PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND WILL NOT INCREASE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING. VOID WHERE PROHIBITED OR RESTRICTED BY LAW.**

---

## 1. Sponsor

This sweepstakes is sponsored by MMAM (My Merch and Music), a nonprofit initiative supporting independent artists worldwide. Official communications will be made via [@MERCHonSolana](https://twitter.com/MERCHonSolana).

---

## 2. Eligibility

The sweepstakes is open to legal residents worldwide who are at least 18 years of age at the time of entry. Void where prohibited or restricted by law. Employees, officers, and directors of MMAM or its affiliates are not eligible to win.

---

## 3. Entry Period

Each entry period begins **12:00 AM CST on Monday (August 04, 2025)** and ends at **11:59 PM CST on Saturday (August 09, 2025)**.

---

## 4. How to Enter

### Method 1: Token Entry

- Send any amount of $MERCH tokens to the **official MMAM wallet address** (posted weekly on [@MERCHonSolana](https://twitter.com/MERCHonSolana)).
- Each valid transaction counts as one entry.
- You may submit multiple entries.
- Zealy XP-based multipliers apply to token-based entries only (see Section 6).

### Method 2: Free Entry

- Complete at least one official MMAM quest through [Zealy](https://zealy.io/c/merchonsolana) during the weekly entry period.
- Free entries must include your **Solana wallet address** and a **working email address** using the provided Zealy submission form.
- Incomplete submissions are ineligible to win.

---

## 5. Prizes

- **Token Prize:** One (1) winner receives 50% of the total token entry pool (in $MERCH).
- **Shirt Prize:** One (1) winner receives a MMAM branded T-shirt. 
- MMAM reserves the right to increase prize quantity or value at its discretion.

---

## 6. XP-Based Entry Multipliers (Token Entries Only)

Your Zealy XP at the end of each week determines your entry multiplier:

| Weekly XP         | Multiplier |
|-------------------|------------|
| 0-49 XP           | 1X         |
| 50-79 XP          | 2X         |
| 80-109 XP         | 3X         |
| 110-139 XP        | 4X         |
| 140+ XP           | 5X         |

- Only token entries are eligible for XP multipliers.
- XP resets weekly and is tracked via Zealy.

---

## 7. Shirt Prize Eligibility

To be eligible for the shirt prize:
- Entrant must have submitted both their **Solana wallet address** and **email address** via the Zealy entry form.
- Shirt winners will be contacted by email to confirm:
  - Shirt size
  - Shipping address

---

## 8. Winner Selection and Notification

- Winners are selected at random from all qualified entries using a verifiable random tool.
- Winners are announced each Sunday on [@MERCHonSolana](https://twitter.com/MERCHonSolana).
- Token prizes will be sent directly to winning wallet addresses where possible.

---

## 9. Unclaimed Prizes

- **Token prize (token entry):** If a wallet is valid, prize will be sent automatically.
- **Token prize (free entry):** If no valid wallet was submitted, the prize will be forfeited after 7 days and will be redrawn.
- **Shirt prize:** If no valid email was submitted, or the winner fails to respond within 7 days of notification, the prize will be forfeited and will not be redrawn.

---

## 10. General Conditions

- MMAM reserves the right to modify, suspend, or cancel the sweepstakes at any time.
- Any attempt to manipulate or abuse the entry system may result in disqualification.
- By participating, you agree to abide by these rules and MMAM's decisions, which are final and binding.

---

## 11. Release and Limitation of Liability

By participating, entrants release MMAM, its affiliates, and their respective officers, employees, and agents from any liability for:
- Entry errors, delays, or malfunctions
- Prize delivery issues
- Any damages arising from participation

---

## 12. Privacy

Any personal data collected will only be used for administering the sweepstakes and will not be sold or shared. Shirt winners' addresses will be used for shipping only.

---

## 13. Governing Law

This sweepstakes is governed by the laws of the State of Texas and applicable U.S. federal law.

---

Join the mission. Support artists. Win rewards.
